constitutional reform and contributed to the search for a
political solution to the conflict in Sri Lanka.
</P>
<P>
Thiruchelvam, considered as a moderate Tamil parliamentarian,
and three others including the suicide bomber were killed in a
suicide bombing Thursday morning in Colombo, capital of Sri Lanka,
informed sources said.  
