<HEADLINE> Results at European Swimming Championships </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISTANBUL, July 30 (Xinhua) -- Following are the finals results
at the European Swimming Championships here on Friday:
</P>
<P>
Men's 200 meters freestyle:
</P>
<P>
