<DOCNO> XIE19990730.0109 </DOCNO>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-30 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> The Awakening of A Falun Gong Practitioner </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Li Yi, former deputy chief of Falun Gong's guidance station in
Zhucheng City, had been deeply involved in the organization.
Though advised to leave, he found himself unable to disentangle
himself from the group.
</P>
<P>
The Party's publication of its policies on Falun Gong, and the
exposures of Falun Gong founder Li Hongzhi's true face, finally
woke him up.
</P>
<P>
"Is Master Li really that respectable," he now asks himself and
his fellow practitioners. Li falsified his date of birth to
coincide with that of Sakyamuni, masterminded his followers'
besieging of Zhongnanhai, the seat of the central government, but
denied he had played any role in this incident.
</P>
<P>
"These two things have made me realize that Li Hongzhi is
really a hypocrite. And where can we find the 'truthfulness,
benevolence, and tolerance' he has been preaching?"
</P>
<P>
Promoters claim that Falun Gong helps cure people's illnesses.
"I had practiced Falun Gong for four years, but there was no
improvement of my skin disease," he said.
</P>
<P>
Under the guise of spreading Falun Gong, Li Hongzhi instigated
practitioners to besiege the Party and government headquarters. "
He pushed us into direct opposition to the government, and hurt us
greatly," he said.
</P>
<P>
Li Yi pleaded for his fellow practitioners to wake up
immediately and stop doing the absurd and being fooled by Li
Hongzhi and his malicious fallacies.
</P>
<P>
In another development, more than 127,000 people in north China
's Hebei Province have made a clear break with Falun Gong and its
malicious cult over the past week. So far, all of the Falun Gong
instruction stations in the province have been closed. More than
149,000 books, 71,000 pieces of publicity materials, 18,000
pictures, and over 10,000 audio and video tapes related to Falun
Gong have been confiscated.
</P>
<P>
In east China's Jiangsu Province, the majority of key Falun
Gong members are reported to have quit the organization. 
</P>
</TEXT>
