<HEADLINE> Indonesia's Former President Allowed to Go Home </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JAKARTA, July 30 (Xinhua) -- Indonesian former president
Soeharto was discharged from the Pertamina Hospital here Friday
after receiving treatment for mild stroke for the past 10 days.
